#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salary_attachment.rst:5
msgid ""
"*Salary attachments* in Odoo refer to a portion of an employee's earnings "
"that are designated for a specific purpose, both voluntary and involuntary. "
"These can include contributions to a retirement plan, repayment of a loan, "
"wage garnishments, or child support."
msgstr ""
"As *penhoras de salĂĄrio* no Odoo se referem a uma parte dos ganhos de um "
"funcionĂĄrio que sĂŁo designados para uma finalidade especĂ­fica, tanto "
"voluntĂĄria quanto involuntĂĄria. Isso pode incluir contribuiĂ§Ă”es para um "
"plano de aposentadoria, pagamento de um emprĂ©stimo ou pensĂŁo alimentĂ­cia."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salary_attachment.rst:9
msgid ""
"Voluntary salary attachments, such as repaying a loan, or contributing to a "
"charity on a monthly basis, are considered *Assignments of Salary* in Odoo. "
"Salary attachments that are required, such as a lawsuit settlement "
"repayment, or repaying a tax lien, are considered *Attachments of Salary* in "
"Odoo. Child support payments have their own category, and are simply "
"referred to as *Child Support* in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Penhoras de salĂĄrio voluntĂĄrios, como o pagamento de um emprĂ©stimo ou a "
"contribuiĂ§ĂŁo mensal para uma instituiĂ§ĂŁo de caridade, sĂŁo considerados "
"*AtribuiĂ§Ă”es de salĂĄrio* no Odoo. Penhoras de salĂĄrio obrigatĂłrias, como o "
"pagamento de um acordo judicial ou a quitaĂ§ĂŁo de uma penhora fiscal, sĂŁo "
"considerados *Embargos de salĂĄrio* no Odoo. Os pagamentos de pensĂŁo "
"alimentĂ­cia para filhos tĂȘm sua prĂłpria categoria e sĂŁo chamados "
"simplesmente de *PensĂŁo alimentĂ­cia* no Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salary_attachment.rst:15
msgid ""
"To view this report, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Reporting --"
"> Salary Attachment Report`. The :guilabel:`Salary Attachment Report` shows "
"all deductions or allocations per employee, organized by payslip, in a "
"default pivot table. The default filter is the end of the current year "
"(:guilabel:`Payslip End Date: (year)`). The employees populate the rows, "
"while the various deductions populate the columns, organized by type of "
"deduction, and further grouped by individual payslip."
msgstr ""
"Para visualizar esse relatĂłrio, navegue atĂ© :menuselection:`app Folha de "
"pagamento --> RelatĂłrios --> RelatĂłrio de penhoras de salĂĄrio`. "
"O :guilabel:`RelatĂłrio de penhoras de salĂĄrio` mostra todas as deduĂ§Ă”es ou "
"alocaĂ§Ă”es por funcionĂĄrio, organizadas por holerite, em uma tabela de pivĂŽ "
"padrĂŁo. O filtro padrĂŁo Ă© o final do ano atual (:guilabel:`Data final do "
"holerite: (ano)`). Os funcionĂĄrios preenchem as linhas, enquanto as diversas "
"deduĂ§Ă”es preenchem as colunas, organizadas por tipo de deduĂ§ĂŁo e agrupadas "
"por holerite."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salary_attachment.rst:22
msgid ""
